widgets_values: A cinematic full body video of a blonde model, wearing a red dress as she's slowly walking down the Las Vegas strip, she slowly moves in perfect rhythm, soft sunlight illuminates the scene

Change Scale by to 1 if you don't want latent upscaling here ↓
Default is scale_by 1.3
The 2nd pass slightly changes the output, personally, I always like the 2nd pass better, feel free to lower the denoise value if you want to stay consistent with the original
